  <section>
    <h2>Accessibility Notes</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Include fallback text</strong>: Content between tags is shown if meter is not supported</li>
      <li><strong>Use labels</strong>: Always associate a label with the meter</li>
      <li><strong>Provide context</strong>: Include units or percentages in visible text</li>
      <li><strong>Don't rely on color alone</strong>: Accompany color changes with text indicators</li>
      <li><strong>Screen reader support</strong>: Meters are announced as "X out of Y"</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

